<TEXT>
israeli and palestinian intellectuals signed a 
peace treaty in a symbolic ceremony monday after months of 
arguments and said their example shows that gaps between the two 
sides can be bridged 
if clods like us who are not always very good at taking 
action can do it so can politicians said one of the 
