from that boat says peter i kuniholm a cornell university 
archaeologist and treering expert who is studying pencillike 
cores drilled out of the planks of the 30footlong boat probably 
buried more than 3800 years ago in dashur 
it and three similar boats were buried near the pyramid complex 
